<div><p><p>Write an e-mail that announces a new skill-oriented program at Shikhar IT Solutions. The program will allow workers to share each other’s experience and grow together.</p</p></div><div><strong>Answer:</strong><br><style>body .mathjax_wrap{width: 100%;overflow-x: scroll;margin-bottom:10px;}</style><p>From: admin@shikharitsolutions.com<br />
